1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,107
=Episode 8=

12
00:00:49,540 --> 00:00:50,660
Your Majesty,

13
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:52,299
why are you reviewing

14
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:55,140
the Zhen family case
in the middle of the night?

15
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:57,700
After talking with Xiao Man,

16
00:00:58,260 --> 00:01:00,020
I couldn't sleep.

17
00:01:02,620 --> 00:01:04,019
I think her connection

18
00:01:04,020 --> 00:01:06,340
to the Zhen family

19
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:08,980
runs deeper than I realized.

20
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:12,740
Whenever the Zhen name comes up,

21
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:16,020
she loses focus.

22
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,540
She even took the initiative
to investigate the case.

23
00:01:19,140 --> 00:01:20,260
Duanmu Zhi,

24
00:01:20,860 --> 00:01:23,140
I want to see all the treasures

25
00:01:23,580 --> 00:01:26,180
confiscated in that raid,
especially the Zhen family's

26
00:01:26,380 --> 00:01:28,007
paintings and personal journals.

27
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:30,940
Your Majesty,

28
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:33,380
after the Zhen couple were executed,

29
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:35,660
the palace officials
inventoried their assets.

30
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:38,860
Aside from the ancestral
home and furnishings,

31
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:44,020
there was only this one item left,
a portrait of General Xiao Congrong.

32
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,460
Recently,

33
00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:59,059
a mysterious force

34
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:01,300
has been impeding our plans.

35
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:05,340
The situation at court is unstable.

36
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,680
On the surface, it looks
like a power struggle

37
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,259
between the Grand Princess
and the Emperor,

38
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,219
but in truth,

39
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:12,019
the pressure is being directed at us.

40
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:14,740
Your influence has been quietly eroded.

41
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:15,819
If this continues,

42
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:17,740
it will jeopardize...

43
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:19,180
That's exactly why

44
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:21,820
I had Xiao Man brought back
to the palace.

45
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:25,780
The decade of training Xiao Man

46
00:02:26,140 --> 00:02:29,020
has undergone will surely allow
her to manage palace affairs adeptly.

47
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:30,419
I'm just concerned...

48
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:31,580
Concerned about what?

49
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:34,380
Her relationship with the young emperor?

50
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:39,700
I'm worried she'll be exposed.

51
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:41,620
After all, her face is

52
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:44,500
too much like hers.

53
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,060
Your Majesty,

54
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,340
you haven't slept all night.

55
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:03,740
You should get some rest.

56
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,260
I can't sleep.

57
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:08,780
Duanmu Zhi, be honest with me.

58
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:09,979
If Xiao Congrong really

59
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,940
has deep ties to Xiao Man,

60
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:14,099
then her return to the capital now...

61
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:16,820
Most likely to seek revenge on you.

62
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,020
Nonsense.

63
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:21,460
Put yourself in her shoes.

64
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,979
If someone killed my family,

65
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,659
I'd probably want to take it out

66
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:27,580
on their child too.

67
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:29,740
What am I supposed to do then?

68
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,340
What else?

69
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,299
Strike first.

70
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,740
Kill her.

71
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:36,020
Absolutely not!

72
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,740
Is there any other way?

73
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,220
Then there's nothing left to do.

74
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:42,460
Just lie down

75
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,900
and wait for her to come and kill you.

76
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:49,580
Lie down and wait for her...

77
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:55,979
Though, she probably couldn't
bring herself to hurt you either.

78
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:57,700
Once feelings get involved,

79
00:03:57,940 --> 00:03:59,539
who knows?

80
00:03:59,540 --> 00:04:00,739
Duanmu Zhi,

81
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,380
stop spouting nonsense.

82
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:05,100
You're getting my imagination
running wild.

83
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,940
What did I say?

84
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,939
There's something that doesn't add up.

85
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:12,379
If Xiao Man really were Zhen Mujun,

86
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:14,659
why wouldn't she go to greater lengths
to hide who she is?

87
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:15,379
It must be because

88
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:16,579
of our childhood bond.

89
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:18,059
She warned me about
the border movements

90
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,179
and helped me at every turn.

91
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:19,699
So

92
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:22,300
everything she's done has
been her way of telling me

93
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,420
that her intentions are genuine.

94
00:04:25,980 --> 00:04:28,299
Or could it be a calculated move?

95
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,539
Drawing you in,

96
00:04:29,540 --> 00:04:31,580
only to strike a fatal blow
at the critical moment?

97
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:36,460
She was open with me last night.

98
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:39,540
Today, I want to speak to her openly,
heart to heart.

99
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,239
I want to ask her if she...

100
00:04:41,239 --> 00:04:42,780
What do you wish to
ask me, Your Majesty?

101
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:50,060
What was it Your Majesty
wished to ask me?

102
00:04:52,660 --> 00:04:54,940
(Ask her why she came back.)

103
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:00,900
I wanted to ask you...

104
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,660
(Just say it, Your Majesty.)

105
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:04,700
What I wanted to ask is...

106
00:05:04,980 --> 00:05:06,300
Please go on, Your Majesty.

107
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:08,580
I wanted to ask you...

108
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,660
Yes?

109
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:13,780
(A clean cut is better
than long torment!)

110
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:16,380
I wanted to know...

111
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:22,300
Do you care about me?

112
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,740
Why would Your Majesty ask that?

113
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:36,180
No reason. I was just asking.

114
00:05:41,660 --> 00:05:42,619
Your Majesty,

115
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:43,960
the memorials have been organized.

116
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,760
They're ready whenever
you wish to review them.

117
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:48,379
I'm exhausted.

118
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:49,980
My head's about to split.

119
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,820
I'll deal with them tomorrow.

120
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,859
So I've missed

121
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,500
quite a show lately.

122
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:07,460
That little eunuch really
hid her identity well.

123
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,799
His Majesty spent all this time with her

124
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,440
and never even realized she was a woman.

125
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:16,660
He was even coaxed into
giving her his personal token.

126
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:20,900
And most interesting of all,

127
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:24,819
she's tied to the annihilation
of the Zhen family.

128
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,380
How interesting.

129
00:06:26,695 --> 00:06:28,374
His Majesty has spent the last ten years

130
00:06:28,375 --> 00:06:29,899
playing dumb while sharpening his claws,

131
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:31,500
impervious to schemes.

132
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:32,700
But this time,

133
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,890
he's finally got a weakness.

134
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:38,100
And once there's a weakness,

135
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,659
there's a way in.

136
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:43,059
If I hadn't noticed that
Xiao Man was too handsome

137
00:06:43,060 --> 00:06:45,580
for an ordinary man

138
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,860
and tipped off Lord Duanmu,

139
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:48,779
he might never

140
00:06:48,780 --> 00:06:50,539
have realized the truth.

141
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,940
Handsome?

142
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:53,619
You think she's handsome?

143
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:55,379
I'm far better-looking than she is.

144
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:56,179
Besides,

145
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:59,300
I've never had
any close contact with her.

146
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:01,580
It's perfectly normal I
wouldn't have noticed.

147
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:05,019
Do I smell jealousy?

148
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,259
Lord Duanmu,

149
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:08,980
you're even getting jealous
over a young lady now?

150
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:11,859
Your Highness,

151
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:14,059
may I continue with
matters of actual importance?

152
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:16,180
Have we not been discussing
actual matters all along?

153
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,339
Go on.

154
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:19,539
A few days ago at Yanbo Parlor,

155
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,459
I crossed paths with Xiao Man.

156
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:23,060
She appears delicate,

157
00:07:23,175 --> 00:07:25,779
but her martial skill runs deep.

158
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:27,139
Her martial skill?

159
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:28,260
Yes.

160
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:30,979
That young eunuch

161
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:33,140
looks like a pawn,

162
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:35,660
but it's highly likely

163
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:38,060
she is one of the players herself.

164
00:07:38,380 --> 00:07:40,940
And a few days before that encounter,

165
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:43,940
I saw her meeting secretly at
Yanbo Parlor with Eunuch Jia,

166
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:46,619
and with someone else

167
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:48,740
in a private chamber.

168
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:50,100
Who?

169
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:53,220
The Prince Consort.

170
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,539
Your Highness,

171
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:01,859
someone has come to see you.

172
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:03,659
They claim to be an old acquaintance.

173
00:08:03,660 --> 00:08:04,780
Leave us.

174
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:12,300
You may go now.

175
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:14,299
From here on, be more careful.

176
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:15,900
Don't let yourselves
be discovered again.

177
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:18,780
Especially you,

178
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:20,739
act with more restraint.

179
00:08:20,740 --> 00:08:22,019
Rest assured, Your Highness.

180
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:24,660
I've always been careful
and very restrained.

181
00:08:27,780 --> 00:08:28,900
This is an accident.

182
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,740
My legs were numb.

183
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:45,740
Your Highness, you promised
me something and never delivered.

184
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:47,900
I had no choice but
to come collect it myself.

185
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,980
Prince Consort, stay where you are.

186
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:01,500
Take one more step,

187
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,739
and don't blame me
for what happens next.

188
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:04,819
How dare you,

189
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,700
abducting the Grand Princess
on Great Qian soil.

190
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:09,819
Easy, Prince Consort.

191
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:11,419
We're only looking to borrow some money

192
00:09:11,420 --> 00:09:12,739
from the Grand Princess.

193
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:14,940
Must we resort to blades?

194
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,380
Very well.

195
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:18,539
How much do you require?

196
00:09:18,540 --> 00:09:19,499
Not much.

197
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:21,539
Just 300,000 taels of silver.

198
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:22,979
300,000?

199
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:25,659
Do you even know what that amount means?

200
00:09:25,660 --> 00:09:27,700
I know you personally can't produce it,

201
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,139
but you oversee

202
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:31,300
the entire imperial
treasury of Great Qian.

203
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:33,700
Surely that wouldn't
be difficult for you.

204
00:09:34,980 --> 00:09:36,100
What's the matter?

205
00:09:36,260 --> 00:09:37,459
You don't want to pay me?

206
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:38,819
Then the Grand Princess

207
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:40,379
will simply have to die by my blade.

208
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:41,380
Wait.

209
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:45,659
It's not that I don't want to pay,
I simply can't produce that amount.

210
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:49,180
I've heard you've been using treasury silver
to fund quite a few dealings for Eunuch Jia.

211
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:52,020
If, as you claim,

212
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:53,299
I have engaged

213
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,179
in numerous transactions
with Director Jia,

214
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:57,059
then the treasury funds
would be with him.

215
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,920
That would make it even
harder for me to pay, wouldn't it?

216
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,379
Why don't you release my wife first?

217
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:02,379
Then we can discuss terms.

218
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:03,500
Sure.

219
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:07,132
I heard you're the finest
martial champion in Great Qian.

220
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:10,100
How about a match with my best warrior?

221
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,424
If you defeat him,

222
00:10:12,425 --> 00:10:14,780
I'll release the Grand Princess.

223
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:19,220
I haven't practiced in years.

224
00:10:19,780 --> 00:10:21,980
But for my wife's sake,

225
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:25,220
I have no choice but to fight.

226
00:10:29,912 --> 00:10:31,607
(Fuling Palace)

227
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:32,780
That's all you got?

228
00:10:36,380 --> 00:10:37,620
He's quite strong.

229
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:40,580
Who said anything about martial match?

230
00:10:40,620 --> 00:10:42,460
I meant a dance match.

231
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:43,780
You...

232
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:45,900
I don't know how to dance.

233
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:47,920
Then I suppose I'll just
finish off the Grand Princess...

234
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:48,700
Don't.

235
00:10:51,740 --> 00:10:52,980
Tell me what you want,

236
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:54,460
I'll do it.

237
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:58,740
I know you're Great Qian's
finest martial champion,

238
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:01,740
but I want to see you
dancing like a woman.

239
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:03,340
The more alluring your dance,

240
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:05,060
the greater my delight.

241
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,540
What's the matter?

242
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,820
You won't do it?
